Colonel Mustafa has finally revealed why he's broken up with his girlfriend of two years because she could not give up her virginity to him before marriage. In an interview with a local TV station, he stated that he prefers having sexual knowledge of his partner before decides to marry the person. “I broke up with the gospel artiste because she insisted that I have
to marry her when she is still a virgin. I told her that I could not
wait for marriage to have sex with her. Before marrying someone, I must
have sexual knowledge of the partner I will spend the rest of my life
with. She could be a man and all through I had been made to believe she
was a woman,” Mustafa said.